7. **Istalgancha matn (satr) qabul qilib, ularning umumiy belgilar sonini qaytaruvchi funksiya yozing.**
def number_point(*text):
	sum=0
	if not text:
		return 'ILtimos kamida 1 ta tekst kiriting!'
	for x in text:
		sum+=len(x)
	return sum
text1=number_point('abdugani', 'farangiz')
text2=number_point()
print(text2)
print(text1)
